/gps/pos/centre 0. 0. -3.2 cm
/gps/pos/halfx 5 cm
/gps/pos/halfy 5 cm




/gps/ang/type iso
/gps/ang/mintheta 0 deg
/gps/ang/maxtheta 90 deg
/gps/ang/minphi 0 deg
/gps/ang/maxphi 360 deg


/gps/ene/type Pow
/gps/ene/alpha -1
/gps/ene/min 0.1 MeV
/gps/ene/max 10 MeV




